PrecisAcceptance of a DESIGNATION wherein the NORWAY HOUSE CREE NATION BAND OF INDIANS surrenders, for a term of 50 years, some 11.5 hectares of land on Norway House Indian Reserve No. 17 in Manitoba, in order to allow them to be leased for commercial, industrial, recreational or residential purposes.
Attachments
precis:
Acceptance of a DESIGNATION wherein the NORWAY HOUSE CREE NATION BAND OF
INDIANS surrenders, for a term of 50 years, some 11.5 hectares of land on
Norway House Indian Reserve No. 17 in Manitoba, in order to allow them to
be leased for commercial, industrial, recreational or residential purposes.
